Welcome to Pasabaya! You've joined a community-driven space built to make carpooling simple, direct, and completely free in the Philippines. Together, we can share the road, split the costs, and help beat the daily traffic.

Visit our website here: https://pasabaya.app

============================================================
GETTING STARTED CHECKLIST
============================================================

1. Verify your profile:
Ensure your registered Facebook profile link is correct. Since Pasabaya is a public board, other members will search and connect with you on Facebook Messenger to coordinate rides.

2. Offer a Ride:
Empty passenger seats on your commute? Post a ride offer specifying your departure time, route, and seat availability.

3. Request a Ride:
Need a ride? Create a request so drivers traveling on your route can find you.


