============================================================
🛡️ STAY SAFE ON THE ROAD
============================================================

Pasabaya is a digital bulletin board, not a transportation company. Always check the other person's Facebook profile details (account age, friends list, activity) before finalizing a trip, and meet in well-lit public spaces.

